        google: { rating: 4.5, review_count: 1477, maps_url: 'https://maps.google.com/?cid=10091604970785504202&g_mp=CiVnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLkdldFBsYWNlEAIYBCAA', reviews: [{author: 'Mj Finest', rating: 5, text: 'Tammy was very knowledgeable and extremely helpful. She took the time to understand what I was looking for and guided me through the options with confidence and care. I was especially pleased with the wide variety of edibles available. Overall, it was a great experience, and I truly appreciated her excellent customer service.', time: 'a month ago'}, {author: 'Dmitriy Mendeleev', rating: 5, text: 'Best bud tenders in the twin cities. Love their selection, and pricing is on point. They were beyond helpful, quick and efficient. I walked out with exactly what i wanted.  Parking was super easy, with plenty of accessibility. Will be coming back regularly', time: '2 months ago'}, {author: 'Teresa Alfuth', rating: 5, text: 'Hey, far aside from the cute hair I had the best cashier Rin - and she knew everything I had to ask and I won an awesome sign too. (They have great products)!This place is so freaking awesome. Five star review!', time: 'a month ago'}, {author: 'Ren Olive', rating: 5, text: 'I came on their opening Friday and the staff managed the line so well! I now go out of my way to stop here when I’m visiting the cities. This dispensary has a welcoming vibe: clean, funky, and has good mood lighting and music. Sabby and Rin helped me out and were lovely folks who made me feel seen and welcomed. I didn’t feel dumb for asking questions. They also have a good rotating selection of ac', time: 'a month ago'}, {author: 'Jo Anna Thomas', rating: 5, text: 'Great.. Use kiosks stand in line get order move along .. Great speedy service nice place you can get your medicine there along with, shirts, hats, bowls, papers etc .. Nice and calm must have ID.... amazing flower....', time: '4 months ago'}] }
