        google: { rating: 4.1, review_count: 136, maps_url: 'https://maps.google.com/?cid=3022178596820853389&g_mp=CiVnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLkdldFBsYWNlEAIYBCAA', reviews: [{author: 'Joshua Collins', rating: 5, text: 'I love legacy cannabis in Woodbury. Everyone at the store is so friendly and helpful. The state tax on cannabis sucks, but their products are the best for what they state allows. I’m sure before we know it the milligrams of thc will be so high we wont be able to finish a whole joint, but im super happy with their eighths of Budd for now.', time: '4 months ago'}, {author: 'Ocean Love', rating: 3, text: 'EDIT: it’s 100% not worth it to pay with Card because instead of being like a normal business and maybe charging like a little bit of a fee they treat it like an ATM So that means they charge you a three dollar service fee on top of rounding to the nearest five dollars  Here’s an example. The item I purchased was $5.99. My card was charged for $10. I was given four dollars back in cash  On top of ', time: '2 months ago'}, {author: 'StarCrumbles', rating: 5, text: 'So confused by some of the negative reviews! I have been to this dispensary regularly for several months, and I’ve always been impressed by their selection of flower. Industry is still ramping up. I am assuming the prices will go down eventually. I’m originally from California and remember the early days of the recreational market. It was a little slow-going at first.  Picked up a great selection ', time: '2 months ago'}, {author: 'Ghostly Names', rating: 5, text: 'Absolutely love the vibes. Very nostalgic environment.  The staff was super helpful and very friendly.  Prices are reasonable and rhe product choices are top notch. They just treat you like a person and not a number, you can tell they genuinely care about your needs. Definitely going to recommend. Parking is also very easy and wheelchair friendly', time: '2 months ago'}, {author: 'Jens Bach', rating: 5, text: 'Wonderful customer service. I actually found the exact same Gorilla Glue #4 strain I’ve been hunting down for 5+ years. Same taste, smell, look, everything. Beyond happy. Thank you!', time: 'a month ago'}] }
