        google: { rating: 4.7, review_count: 63, maps_url: 'https://maps.google.com/?cid=16134270424750811827&g_mp=CiVnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLkdldFBsYWNlEAIYBCAA', reviews: [{author: 'Dave Raymond', rating: 5, text: 'Quality team, quality products. I met Keith, Tony, Brian, Mona, + one additional talented individual. Knowledge and attention to detail is excellent.  Price, well a little higher than expected, but there is nothing like operating profit to smooth out the inevitable bumps a small business encounters.', time: 'a month ago'}, {author: 'Beth Londer', rating: 5, text: 'I feel that the guys doing this ARE doing this for the love of the product and not just for the dollar. You can definitely tell the difference between this place and the corporates like Green Goods and Rise. These guys stand behind their products. I feel that if I didn\'t like something. I could totally bring it back and feel okay about it. I feel like they know and love what they are doing. And to', time: '3 months ago'}, {author: 'shad haines', rating: 5, text: 'I stopped in having no idea what I wanted or needed. The employees were so kind, patient and very helpful to say the least. They were extremely knowledgeable, needless to say I walked out a happy camper. They have a wide selection of quality products their employees customer service far surpassed my expectations. If this is what you\'re into I highly recommend them. Not to mention the owners Totall', time: '3 months ago'}, {author: 'GreenthumbMN', rating: 1, text: 'I think they mean "higher price" not "higher place" $130 for a quarter of flower is outrageous. If you are into hemp stuff or cbd products this is the right place for you, but if you are looking for actual recreational cannabis... there is better spots around. If you check out rise or greengoods you can get hooked up with a free med card to avoid taxes and get a better variety of products for less', time: '3 months ago'}, {author: 'michael formisano', rating: 5, text: 'I was just in the store buying a vape. After I bought it, the vape did not work. However, the staff and manager could not have been more nicer, as they helped me figure out a solution and even replaced the broken vape! 10 out of 10 service I cannot recommend this place more!', time: 'a month ago'}] }
